1
00:00:04,880 --> 00:00:05,760
Baby.

2
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:11,200
I'm telling you, I'm so mad today.

3
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:14,120
This Wang Jun is really bad.

4
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:16,120
We didn't have to work hard anymore.

5
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:19,800
Baby, where are you?

6
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:23,650
I've been talking for a long time and you haven't said a word.

7
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:32,080
Bro.

8
00:00:32,080 --> 00:00:33,480
Where is the watch? Give it back.

9
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:35,210
The watch was bought by my boss.

10
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:36,320
Hengfa Pawnshop.

11
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:37,680
His name is Wang Jun.

12
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,530
How much did you sell it for?

13
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:40,840
Two hundred.

14
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,880
Two hundred?

15
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,200
Do you think I'm a fool?

16
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:46,520
Really. He only gave me two hundred.

17
00:00:46,720 --> 00:00:48,680
I robbed you, and he robbed me.

18
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:50,720
I had no choice. Really.

19
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:53,240
Two hundred, right?

20
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,040
Here is four hundred.

21
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,280
Buy it back for me.

22
00:00:58,680 --> 00:00:59,200
No.

23
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,440
Bro,

24
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:01,840
let me go.

25
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:04,200
He wouldn't sell it to me no matter how much money I offer.

26
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,319
I can't get it back.

27
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,080
It's useless to kill me.

28
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:09,280
Really. I can't afford to mess with him.

29
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,940
He has a powerful background.

30
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,060
He has a powerful background, right?

31
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,640
You robbed me,

32
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,000
and he robbed you.

33
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,600
Then I have to rob him.

34
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,880
Anyone who can open a shop in a place like that

35
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:27,010
is definitely not an ordinary person.

36
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,330
Am I an ordinary person?

37
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,440
Hengfa Pawnshop.

38
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,200
Hengfa Pawnshop.

39
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,000
Wang Jun.

40
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,920
Take care, bro.

41
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,480
It's been so many days.

42
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:14,140
Don't you have a word of truth?

43
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,060
Where exactly is Hua Weihong?

44
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:17,610
How would I know where he is?

45
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,320
Why don't you ask him?

46
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,640
Time to eat.

47
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,640
You are finally back.

48
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:24,880
What did you buy?

49
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:27,520
Kung Pao Chicken.

50
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,560
Smells so good.

51
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:32,000
I'm not hungry. I have no appetite.

52
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:34,360
As a public servant, you can't waste food.

53
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:36,240
If you don't eat it, I'll give it to him.

54
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,079
Give him one.

55
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,680
It's terrible.

56
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,680
Have you guys ever eaten anything good?

57
00:02:57,920 --> 00:03:01,000
I've had Kung Pao Chicken a hundred times better than this.

58
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,800
This uses regular cooking wine.

59
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:05,560
Normally, it should use Shaoxing yellow wine.

60
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:07,640
Peanuts should be fried in advance.

61
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,860
Then added to the wok before serving.

62
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:12,040
The sauce is also particular.

63
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:14,860
It needs to be sour, sweet, salty, and spicy.

64
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:17,760
When stir-frying the chicken, use high heat.

65
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:20,420
Finally, pour the sauce over it before serving.

66
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,000
That's how it should be.

67
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:25,160
Which restaurant makes Kung Pao Chicken like this?

68
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:26,360
You're talking nonsense again, aren't you?

69
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:28,960
Hao You Lai's Kung Pao Chicken is made this way.

70
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:31,200
Hao You Lai?

71
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:34,160
He's telling the truth this time.

72
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,200
I've actually heard of this Hao You Lai.

73
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,560
Is it the one in that alley?

74
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,280
Is the chef named Master Li?

75
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,560
What Master Li?

76
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,840
Master Chen. His surname is Chen.

77
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:46,240
Are you talking about Haoyoulai Restaurant in Guangnan?

78
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,160
It's not Haoyoulai in Guangnan.

79
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,660
It should be Haoyoulai Restaurant in Guixi,

80
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:55,360
because his hometown is in Guixi.

81
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,400
Let's go.

82
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,640
Let's find Master Chen and have something fresh.

83
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,960
Have something fresh?

84
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:24,960
I got it back.

85
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,400
Let's go.

86
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:42,240
What are you doing? Who are you?

87
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:44,880
Let go.

88
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,020
Who are you?

89
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,440
Let go.

90
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,360
Stop. Stop hitting.

91
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,040
Stop hitting. Behave.

92
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:56,840
Stop hitting.

93
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,220
Sister Qin.

94
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,480
Don't pull this crap with me.

95
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:12,240
You're quite the pretender.

96
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,200
Sister Qin.

97
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:17,280
Look at this bastard, he's exactly as I described.

98
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:19,680
He's full of it. Good thing you came in time,

99
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,160
otherwise they would have run away.

100
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,360
That's a lot of money.

101
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,040
Take the money.

102
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,440
Let my woman go.

103
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,290
Are you guys in the game too?

104
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:39,200
Sister, they're not in the game.

105
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,770
They're two wanted criminals.

106
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,480
Pretty wild.

107
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:47,159
Sister, look at the big haul we got today.

108
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:49,120
Don't I get a little credit for it?

109
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:54,120
That watch, Brother Jun bought it from me for 200 yuan during the day.

110
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,960
I... 200 yuan, I...

111
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:58,200
If you like it, just take it.

112
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,600
Stop your nonsense.

113
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,260
Thank you, Sister Qin.

114
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:09,560
Wanted man, you scared me to death.

115
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,840
You have the watch. Don't talk nonsense outside.

116
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,300
Understood. Understood.

117
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,890
Which hand touched my husband?

118
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:21,760
This one?

119
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,520
I will play with you.

120
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,280
When you touched my husband,

121
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,960
did you ask who I am?

122
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:43,610
You want to play, right?

123
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:46,400
I'll play with you until you've had enough.

124
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,770
Is Master Chen Danian here?

125
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,120
Are you here to eat or...

126
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,850
We are looking for Chen Danian.

127
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,490
Honey, someone is looking for you.

128
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,090
Who is it?

129
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:03,640
Are you two eating?

130
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,440
Take a seat anywhere.

131
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,400
Honey, please serve them.

132
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,930
You are Chen Danian, right?

133
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:08,600
Police.

134
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,760
We have some questions for you.

135
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,290
Sit down.

136
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:11,960
Okay.

137
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:18,320
Mr. Chen, sorry to bother you.

138
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:19,280
I want to ask you about something.

139
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:19,840
Go ahead.

140
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,900
Have some people been here recently?

141
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:23,650
Comrade.

142
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,680
I run a restaurant.

143
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:27,440
It's full of people all day long.

144
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,760
Business is pretty good.

145
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,520
Pretty good.

146
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,640
Not bad.

147
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,680
Then recommend something to me.

148
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,680
What are your specialties?

149
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,640
Like signature dishes.

150
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,500
Kung Pao Chicken. Every table orders it.

151
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,320
Hua Weihong also loves Kung Pao Chicken, right?

152
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,320
No, no, no, he...

153
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,840
Is there such a dish?

154
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,320
What dish are you talking about?

155
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,440
I didn't mean a dish.

156
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,640
I meant a person named Hua Weihong.

157
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,840
Uh...

158
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,640
Hua what Hong?

159
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:58,440
Hua Weihong.

160
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,700
Think about it.

161
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:05,360
Hua Weihong, Lu San, Cao Aiyuan.

162
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,040
You know these three, right?

163
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,100
Didn't they come here a while ago?

164
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,720
Let me think.

165
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,560
Hua... Hua what San?

166
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:21,240
Comrade, you spoke too fast, I...

167
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:25,480
I'm getting old and my hearing isn't very good.

168
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:28,040
You look quite sharp and energetic to me.

169
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:30,240
It's a bit noisy outside your place.

170
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,970
What do you think, Officer Lin?

171
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:33,559
The station is quiet.

172
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,919
The station is quiet.

173
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,679
Let's go back and investigate. Go.

174
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:40,080
Officer.

175
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,520
I know.

176
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,570
I know where Hua Weihong is.

177
00:08:59,240 --> 00:08:59,760
Are you okay?

178
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,360
I'm fine.

179
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,120
This old house must be ten or twenty years old.

180
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,840
More than that.

181
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:11,100
Isn't this your place? Which one?

182
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:14,480
Which one? I haven't been here in so long, I forgot.

183
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,040
You forgot your own home?

184
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,440
Where are my keys?

185
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:19,120
Stop playing tricks, will you?

186
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:19,880
I'm not.

187
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,680
Here they are.

188
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,480
Wait, this seems...

189
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,440
Hurry up, stop stalling.

190
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,280
I'm not.

191
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,700
Nobody's here.

192
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:03,960
Mr. Chen.

193
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,160
If they contact you again,

194
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:07,760
remember to call the police.

195
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,160
You can go now.

196
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:11,960
We still need to keep searching.

197
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,440
Okay.

198
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,200
Close the door when you leave.

199
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,080
Don't worry.

200
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:28,160
Is anyone there?

201
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,560
No.

202
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:45,520
Is anyone there?

203
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:49,400
Who is it? Do you know what time it is? Aren't you sleeping?
